# Find OGRE includes and library
#
# This module defines
#  OGRE_INCLUDE_DIRS
#  OGRE_LIBRARIES, the libraries to link against to use OGRE.
#  OGRE_LIBRARY_DIRS, the location of the libraries
#  OGRE_FOUND, If false, do not try to use OGRE
